data.description: New Construction by D.R. Horton! Welcome to the Charleston in Grandview Park. This beautiful paired villa features 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, den, open concept great room, dining and kitchen. Nine foot ceilings throughout. Kitchen features breakfast bar, quartz counters, pantry, tall 42inch cabinets with crown molding and top of the line flooring. Bathroom 1 boasts beautiful ceramic tiled shower, double sinks, two walk in closets and split bedroom design for privacy. Covered porch for enjoying the outdoors in this low maintenance community. Community convenient to all the area has to offer with shopping, dining, parks and more. All D.R. Horton Indianapolis homes include our America's Smart Home® Technology.
